<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Flavourrr By Yannick</title>

<style>
body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    background: #f8f8f8;
}

header {
    background: #111;
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 60px 20px;
}

header h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin: 0;
}

header p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
}

section {
    padding: 50px 20px;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: auto;
}

.menu {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 20px;
}

.card {
    background: white;
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,.1);
}

.price {
    color: #d35400;
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 20px;
}

.contact {
    background: #111;
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
}

footer {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
    <h1>Flavourrr By Yannick</h1>
    <p>Homemade African & Caribbean Food</p>
</header>

<section>
    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p>
        Welcome to Flavourrr By Yannick.
        We serve delicious homemade African and Caribbean meals
        prepared with fresh ingredients and authentic flavours.
    </p>
</section>

<section>
    <h2>Our Menu</h2>

    <div class="menu">

        <div class="card">
            <h3>Jollof Rice & Beef</h3>
            <p>Traditional West African jollof rice served with tender beef.</p>
            <p class="price">£20</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h3>Creamy Chicken Pasta</h3>
            <p>Rich creamy pasta with seasoned chicken.</p>
            <p class="price">£20</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h3>Chicken & Rice Box</h3>
            <p>Roasted chicken breast with rice and vegetables.</p>
            <p class="price">£20</p>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>

<section class="contact">
    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>Email: flavourrrbyyannick@gmail.com</p>
    <p>Instagram: @flavourrrbyyannick</p>
</section>

<footer>
    <p>© 2026 Flavourrr By Yannick. All Rights Reserved.</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
